description:
These trail-ready pants offer plenty of pockets, so you're always prepared. A relaxed fit and stretch fabric makes them a comfortable choice for do-it-all backcountry enthusiasts. Quick dry materials with a DWR finish help you stay dry on canoe trips, crag sessions, or days on the trail.Stretch nylon fabric is comfortable and durable in urban or backcountry environments.Fabric is quick-drying with a DWR finish.Belt loops with a zip fly and button closure.Jeans-like hand pockets and top stitched rear pockets.2 large cargo pockets provide extra storage.Relaxed wide leg, articulated knees and gussetted crotch allow unrestricted movement.

